[{"title":"Hexo博客初步搭建","url":"/2022/hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/hexo%E7%AB%99%E7%82%B9%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%B0%E5%BD%95/","content":"<p>参考文章：</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/26625249/\">https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/26625249\\</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/60578464\">https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/60578464</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"搭建计划：\"><a href=\"#搭建计划：\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"搭建计划：\"></a>搭建计划：</h2><ul>\n<li><input checked=\"\" disabled=\"\" type=\"checkbox\"> 设定主题为next</li>\n<li><input checked=\"\" disabled=\"\" type=\"checkbox\"> 版权声明</li>\n<li><input checked=\"\" disabled=\"\" type=\"checkbox\"> 导航栏配置</li>\n<li><input checked=\"\" disabled=\"\" type=\"checkbox\"> 侧边栏头像</li>\n<li><input disabled=\"\" type=\"checkbox\"> 侧边栏社交小图标-b站未完成</li>\n<li><input checked=\"\" disabled=\"\" type=\"checkbox\"> 显示阅读进度</li>\n<li><input checked=\"\" disabled=\"\" type=\"checkbox\"> 增加搜索功能</li>\n<li><input checked=\"\" disabled=\"\" type=\"checkbox\"> 修改文章底部标签图标</li>\n<li><input checked=\"\" disabled=\"\" type=\"checkbox\"> 文章末尾增加本文结束</li>\n<li><input checked=\"\" disabled=\"\" type=\"checkbox\"> 网站底部增加访问量</li>\n<li><input checked=\"\" disabled=\"\" type=\"checkbox\"> 增加字数统计</li>\n<li><input checked=\"\" disabled=\"\" type=\"checkbox\"> 设置网站的图标</li>\n<li><input checked=\"\" disabled=\"\" type=\"checkbox\"> 博文置顶配置</li>\n<li><input disabled=\"\" type=\"checkbox\"> 代码复制</li>\n<li><input disabled=\"\" type=\"checkbox\"> </li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"解决方案\"><a href=\"#解决方案\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"解决方案\"></a>解决方案</h2><p>将hexo根目录下的.deploy_git/删除掉，然后使用hexo deploy重新部署就可以了。<br>但是暂时不清楚是什么原因引起的错误。</p>\n<p>可以hexo d但是在打开网站后只能看到readme文件。</p>\n<p>原因在于没有设置默认分支为master。自动建立了一个main branch。</p>\n<p>在设置中设置默认分支，并删除掉main branch。</p>\n<p>删除.deploy_git，并重新hexo d</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://picgo-ry.obs.cn-south-1.myhuaweicloud.com/1662046825295-7e21c2e8-9190-4735-8547-7d58502824a3.png\" alt=\"img\"></p>\n<p>现在可以在<a href=\"https://rongyel.github.io/\">https://rongyel.github.io/</a></p>\n<p>看到自己的博客界面啦。</p>\n<p>更换为next主题后，本地服务可以看到页面已经换了</p>\n<p>但是.io的页面还是原来的样子。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://picgo-ry.obs.cn-south-1.myhuaweicloud.com/1662047399987-fa958900-f5f9-47cf-b8ea-4bf4f7a17989.png\" alt=\"img\"></p>\n<p>npm install hexo-renderer-pug hexo-renderer-stylus –save</p>\n<p>安装以后再hexo d</p>\n<p>不知道为什么就可以了。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://picgo-ry.obs.cn-south-1.myhuaweicloud.com/1662047471308-3cd2c599-ad34-4c5a-8557-b253bbbfcd35.png\" alt=\"img\"></p>\n<p>每次hexo d推送之前，最好先清除浏览器的缓存。不然会发现没有变化。</p>\n<p>因为我已经搭建好图床了，所以从语雀移植过来的图片需要进行重新上传。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/351031589\">https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/351031589</a></p>\n<p>对自己的页面进行一些配置</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/28128674\">https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/28128674</a></p>\n<p>改变图标</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/qq_43340547/article/details/120581558\">https://blog.csdn.net/qq_43340547/article/details/120581558</a></p>\n<p>总是不成功……b站的图标一直没搞出来</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://picgo-ry.obs.cn-south-1.myhuaweicloud.com/bilibili.svg\" alt=\"bilibili\"></p>\n<p>算了，搞不定</p>\n<p>添加搜索功能</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.jianshu.com/p/fdd8e4e36c57\">https://www.jianshu.com/p/fdd8e4e36c57</a></p>\n<p>这个教程有问题</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/weixin_45877759/article/details/107141789\">https://blog.csdn.net/weixin_45877759/article/details/107141789</a></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://picgo-ry.obs.cn-south-1.myhuaweicloud.com/image-20220903011954966.png\" alt=\"image-20220903011954966\"></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/as480133937/article/details/100138838\">https://blog.csdn.net/as480133937/article/details/100138838</a></p>\n<p>配置了很久以后，发现自己的next版本太旧了，很多修改方式都对不上。无语了，</p>\n<p>浪费了好多时间啊。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/theme-next/hexo-theme-next\">https://github.com/theme-next/hexo-theme-next</a></p>\n<p>设置近期文章</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.cnblogs.com/cscshi/p/15196107.html\">https://www.cnblogs.com/cscshi/p/15196107.html</a></p>\n<p>增加评论功能</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/weixin_48927364/article/details/123321038\">https://blog.csdn.net/weixin_48927364/article/details/123321038</a></p>\n<p>后面这个更准确</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.jianshu.com/p/b5f509f25872\">https://www.jianshu.com/p/b5f509f25872</a></p>\n<p>关闭特点页面评论的方法</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://roddypy.com/2020/09/18/Hexo-%E5%85%B3%E9%97%AD%E6%96%87%E7%AB%A0%E8%AF%84%E8%AE%BA%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95/\">http://roddypy.com/2020/09/18/Hexo-%E5%85%B3%E9%97%AD%E6%96%87%E7%AB%A0%E8%AF%84%E8%AE%BA%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95/</a></p>\n<p>增加rss</p>\n<p>需要补充</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.dazhuanlan.com/appleking2003/topics/1441463\">https://www.dazhuanlan.com/appleking2003/topics/1441463</a></p>\n<p>一直不成功</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://picgo-ry.obs.cn-south-1.myhuaweicloud.com/image-20220904114335282.png\" alt=\"image-20220904114335282\"></p>\n<p>其实已经成功了，只是我不明白rss的工作原理。</p>\n<p>在谷歌浏览器安装RSS阅读插件就可以看到了。</p>\n<p>b站图标问题还是没有能够解决</p>\n<p>我靠我终于解决了这个问题！！！</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://picgo-ry.obs.cn-south-1.myhuaweicloud.com/image-20220904174552260.png\" alt=\"image-20220904174552260\"></p>\n<p>网络上搜到的办法没一个成功的！！！最后我自己灵机一动搞定了！！！！</p>\n<p>无语了，<a href=\"https://fontawesome.com/icons/bilibili?s=&amp;f=brands\">https://fontawesome.com/icons/bilibili?s=&amp;f=brands</a></p>\n<p>其实这个b站的图标，在最新的fontawesome网站上是有的，</p>\n<p>只是next之类的主题自己默认配置的版本不是最新的，</p>\n<p>要6.0.0的版本才可以。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://picgo-ry.obs.cn-south-1.myhuaweicloud.com/image-20220904174723854.png\" alt=\"image-20220904174723854\"></p>\n<p>可以看到自带的版本是5.13.0的</p>\n<p>我自己设置为6.0.0</p>\n<p>然后<img src=\"https://picgo-ry.obs.cn-south-1.myhuaweicloud.com/image-20220904174756313.png\" alt=\"image-20220904174756313\"></p>\n<p>就可以正常的直接调用该图标了！！！无语了。根本不需要自己添加什么图标文件。</p>\n<h2 id=\"让百度和百度收录博客\"><a href=\"#让百度和百度收录博客\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"让百度和百度收录博客\"></a>让百度和百度收录博客</h2><p><a href=\"https://www.cnblogs.com/lfri/p/12219639.html\">https://www.cnblogs.com/lfri/p/12219639.html</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://craftboss.net/2019/10/23/hexo%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E9%AA%8C%E8%AF%81%E7%99%BE%E5%BA%A6%E7%AB%99%E9%95%BF/\">https://craftboss.net/2019/10/23/hexo%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E9%AA%8C%E8%AF%81%E7%99%BE%E5%BA%A6%E7%AB%99%E9%95%BF/</a></p>\n<p>文件验证的方法</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://picgo-ry.obs.cn-south-1.myhuaweicloud.com/image-20220904190835888.png\" alt=\"image-20220904190835888\"></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/100922816%E4%B8%BB%E5%8A%A8%E6%8E%A8%E9%80%81%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE\">https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/100922816主动推送配置</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.cnblogs.com/MoYu-zc/p/14402037.html\">https://www.cnblogs.com/MoYu-zc/p/14402037.html</a> 主要参考推送设置</p>\n<p>最后使用sitmap的方式进行推送，谷歌必应百度都已经设置完毕了，过几天看看能不能搜索到就好了。</p>\n<p>增加隐藏文章的功能</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/prinsss/hexo-hide-posts/blob/master/README_ZH.md\">https://github.com/prinsss/hexo-hide-posts/blob/master/README_ZH.md</a></p>\n<p>修改文章渲染处理的样式，想改成和typora一样。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://picgo-ry.obs.cn-south-1.myhuaweicloud.com/image-20220905005831797.png\" alt=\"image-20220905005831797\"></p>\n<p>最后发现是查看index文件下就可以知道。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://picgo-ry.obs.cn-south-1.myhuaweicloud.com/image-20220905010301781.png\" alt=\"image-20220905010301781\"></p>\n<p>研究后成功的改变了部署后的页面文章样式可以！</p>\n<p>很好，接下来将typora和hexo的样式修改成一样的，就可以快乐的更新啦。</p>\n","categories":["开发环境"],"tags":["hexo"]},{"title":"Hello World","url":"/2022/%E9%9A%90%E8%97%8F/hello-world/","content":"<p>Welcome to <a href=\"https://hexo.io/\">Hexo</a>! This is your very first post. Check <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/\">documentation</a> for more info. If you get any problems when using Hexo, you can find the answer in <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/troubleshooting.html\">troubleshooting</a> or you can ask me on <a href=\"https://github.com/hexojs/hexo/issues\">GitHub</a>.</p>\n<h2 id=\"Quick-Start\"><a href=\"#Quick-Start\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Quick Start\"></a>Quick Start</h2><h3 id=\"Create-a-new-post\"><a href=\"#Create-a-new-post\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Create a new post\"></a>Create a new post</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo new <span class=\"string\">&quot;My New Post&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>More info: <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/writing.html\">Writing</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"Run-server\"><a href=\"#Run-server\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Run server\"></a>Run server</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo server</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>More info: <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/server.html\">Server</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"Generate-static-files\"><a href=\"#Generate-static-files\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Generate static files\"></a>Generate static files</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo generate</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>More info: <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/generating.html\">Generating</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"Deploy-to-remote-sites\"><a href=\"#Deploy-to-remote-sites\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Deploy to remote sites\"></a>Deploy to remote sites</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo deploy</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>More info: <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/one-command-deployment.html\">Deployment</a></p>\n","categories":["转载"],"tags":["hexo"]},{"title":"typoratest","url":"/2022/%E9%9A%90%E8%97%8F/typoratest/","content":"<h1 id=\"一级标题\"><a href=\"#一级标题\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"一级标题\"></a>一级标题</h1><h2 id=\"二级标题\"><a href=\"#二级标题\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"二级标题\"></a>二级标题</h2><h3 id=\"三级标题\"><a href=\"#三级标题\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"三级标题\"></a>三级标题</h3><h4 id=\"四级标题\"><a href=\"#四级标题\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"四级标题\"></a>四级标题</h4><p><strong>加粗</strong><br>==高亮==<br><em>斜体</em><br><u>下划线</u><br><del>删除线</del></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.runoob.com/css/css-text.html\">https://www.runoob.com/css/css-text.html</a></p>\n<ol>\n<li>有序列表</li>\n</ol>\n<ul>\n<li>无序列表</li>\n</ul>\n","categories":["开发环境"],"tags":["hexo","测试"]},{"title":"ic_list","url":"/2022/%E9%9A%90%E8%97%8F/ic-list/","content":"<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>标题</th>\n<th>单选</th>\n<th>日期</th>\n<th>链接</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td>什么是数字IC工程师</td>\n<td>待开始</td>\n<td>2022-08-27</td>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>GVIM简洁开发环境</td>\n<td>已完成</td>\n<td>2022-08-27</td>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>gvim开发环境梳理+git基本环境</td>\n<td>进行中</td>\n<td>2022-08-29</td>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>typora markdown笔记环境</td>\n<td>已完成</td>\n<td>2022-08-30</td>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Gvim配置.vimrc文件整理 + windows环境配置</td>\n<td>已完成</td>\n<td>2022-08-31</td>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>搭建hexo博客环境</td>\n<td>已完成</td>\n<td>2022-09-01</td>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>配置HEXO博客环境</td>\n<td>已完成</td>\n<td>2022-09-02</td>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>完成hexo博客环境</td>\n<td>已完成</td>\n<td>2022-09-04</td>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n","categories":["开发环境"],"tags":["hexo","记录"]}]